Create table with all outbreak data for a particular pathogen

Source: R/outbreak_table.R
outbreak_table.Rd

Create table with all outbreak data for a particular pathogen

Usage

outbreak_table(df, pathogen)

Arguments

df

processed data with outbreak information produced by data_outbreak_table()

pathogen

name of pathogen

Value

returns flextable summarising all extracted outbreaks for the specified pathogen

Examples

df <- data_outbreak_table(pathogen = "marburg")
#> Rows: 23 Columns: 24
